{"tid":439524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿伯黑麻麻火機照明　辣着床褥燒傷背脊","createTime":"2017-10-18T01:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T03:06:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bae66389ee4094644ff3d638ef44d29f07fc1555","tid":439524,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/photo/bkn-20171018051708718-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171018080351\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171018051708718-1018_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171018080351&h=9fad94d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿伯用打火機照明，意外辣著雜物起火燒埋床褥，阿伯走唔切背部燒傷。現場葵涌葵芳邨葵正樓一單位，事發今晨3時許，60餘歲老翁在房內用打火機照明，惟卻辣着房內雜物，繼而著火焚燒，老翁走避不及背部被火灼傷，家人聞訊走出視察，見發生火警，立即將火撲熄，並報警求助，消防員接報到場，火己被救熄，調查火警無可疑，受傷老翁送院治療，事件中毋須疏散。"},{"pid":"bd30124081bd530d2ee3d186a65adfd25d530860","tid":439524,"uid":69064,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"我後生果陣住木屋無電都係咁啦 驚咩呀"},{"pid":"80241b4fec61c377acf406c8d8caf074cf252ffc","tid":439524,"uid":13355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:39:55.000Z","msg":"佢以為自己古人呀，佢唔鑿壁偷光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07daa5ae5caf8807f1170a28493a952e3d57012","tid":439524,"uid":58354,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:58:07.000Z","msg":"阿伯照明唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe887713c4b67ecdd0d33d5c0c4b592614993383","tid":439524,"uid":11962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:01:11.000Z","msg":"我賽跑冠軍黎嫁嘛"},{"pid":"a244b5b39cf2a6caf9bf860af1abba4132c1df04","tid":439524,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"一百歲唔死，都有新聞睇"},{"pid":"56b56926feb0768a7e427d19f010591c02eea67f","tid":439524,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score